{{Quote|There's a big race tomorrow, on Boonta Eve.|[[Anakin Skywalker]], to [[Qui-Gon Jinn]]|<ref name="Episode 1">{{Film|I}}</ref>}}
'''Boonta Eve''' was an [[Standard year|annual]] [[Hutt]] holiday and festival celebrated on the [[desert]] [[planet]] of [[Tatooine]] during the last [[Standard decade|decades]] of the [[Galactic Republic|Old Republic]]<ref name="AEYNtK" /> and the time of the [[New Republic]].<ref name="Chapter 18">{{TheMandalorian|Chapter 18: The Mines of Mandalore}}</ref> It honored the rise of [[Boonta Hestilic Shad'ruu]] to [[Deity|godhood]].<ref name="AEYNtK" /> In [[Mos Eisley]], it was celebrated with [[fireworks]].<ref name="Chapter 18" /> Just outside [[Mos Espa]] the annual [[Boonta Eve Classic]] race was held to commemorate the holiday.<ref name="Boonta Eve Classic Podracer Pilots">{{Databank|boonta-eve-classic-podracer-pilots|Boonta Eve Classic Podracer Pilots}}</ref>

